WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:22.300
 (applause)

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:26.400
 ♪ (soft music)

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:30.460
 ♪ Rice happy he who hides from pomp and power

00:00:30.460 --> 00:00:34.000
 ♪ In silven shade or solitary bower

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:37.800
 ♪ Where balmy zephyrs fan his burning cheeks

00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:41.780
 - Clown, king of clowns, leave the stage at once!

00:00:41.780 --> 00:00:44.240
 ♪ (dramatic music)

00:00:44.240 --> 00:00:46.680
 - Who is it? - It's Cyrano.

00:00:46.680 --> 00:00:47.780
 - I was afraid he'd do this.

00:00:47.780 --> 00:00:51.320
 ♪ Rice happy he who hides from pomp and power

00:00:51.320 --> 00:00:52.460
 - Wretch!

00:00:52.460 --> 00:00:54.860
 Did I not forbid you to appear this month?

00:00:54.860 --> 00:00:58.020
 ♪ (dramatic music)

00:00:58.020 --> 00:01:00.560
 - Yes, be quiet! - Quiet!

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:02.500
 - Go on, Loperine.

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:04.600
 ♪ (dramatic music)

00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:08.400
 - Rice happy he who, he who indeed!

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:10.980
 Donkey say rather hee-haw!

00:01:10.980 --> 00:01:13.580
 ♪ (dramatic music)

00:01:13.580 --> 00:01:15.040
 Be gone!

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:18.080
 Or must I come and help you off the stage myself?

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:21.420
 ♪ (dramatic music)

00:01:21.420 --> 00:01:22.760
 What?

00:01:22.760 --> 00:01:24.560
 Still there?

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:25.420
 ♪ (dramatic music)

00:01:25.420 --> 00:01:28.560
 - Where balmy zephyrs fan his burning cheek?

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:32.400
 - Fat swine, if you dare breathe one balmy zephyr more,

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.960
 I'll fan your cheeks for you!

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:36.700
 - Play, Sears, if you will protect me.

00:01:36.700 --> 00:01:38.360
 - Proceed, proceed. - Go on.

00:01:38.360 --> 00:01:41.100
 - Sir, I will not allow you to insult me in this manner.

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:42.240
 - Really?

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:44.080
 What manner would you prefer?

00:01:44.080 --> 00:01:45.500
 - Quiet down there!

00:01:45.500 --> 00:01:48.280
 We'll tolerate no more of this!

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:49.820
 Go on with the play, Montfleury.

00:01:49.820 --> 00:01:52.820
 (all clamoring)

00:01:52.820 --> 00:01:54.680
 - Unless these gentlemen retain their seats,

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:57.060
 my sword may bite their ribbons.

00:01:57.060 --> 00:01:59.620
 Who is this braggart?

